        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Been looking into this a little bit. As mentioned, the issue is entirely due to plugins not closing uv handles. Many of these handles are intended to live as long as the Neovim process, so the only way to avoid the hang is to close them in a `VimLeavePre` autocmd.\r\n\r\nShould we really be expecting plugins to close uv handles themselves, or should Neovim close all of them on exit?",
